column5: went to lake joseph this morning , took the 500cc atve with the new track kit on it, wasnt sure how it would do 18 inches of snow 4 inches of slush and 18 inches of ice, went about 2 miles shunted the guys out the bike work amazing no slow or getting stucka t all just did the job and made a path for the guys to walk back, with six guys we had 18 lake trout biggest 7 lbs next was five then a bunch in the 3 lb  also a couple of over sized minnow trout , released almost all of them. great day .
Sounds like you had a succesfull outing! 18 Trout ain't too shabby either.
